---
---
<section class="bg-white py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl">

    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">What business owners notice first</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600">Not prettier pages — more booked jobs and returning clients.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-orange-100 flex items-center justify-center">
            <img src="/logos/artilate-logo.svg" class="w-6 h-6 object-contain" loading="lazy" alt=""/>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-medium text-gray-900 text-sm">Artilate Chocolate</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Retail · Alberta</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-700 italic leading-relaxed text-sm">
          "What changed was not the site — it was the client flow. We finally had structured follow-up and repeat purchase triggers."
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gray-200 flex items-center justify-center">
            <img src="/logos/grillsguard-logo.avif" class="w-6 h-6 object-contain" loading="lazy" alt=""/>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-medium text-gray-900 text-sm">GrillsGuard</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Service · Calgary</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-700 italic leading-relaxed text-sm">
          "Booking behavior improved once reminders and follow-ups were automated. Less manual chasing, more confirmed jobs."
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gray-200 flex items-center justify-center">
            <img src="/logos/gaplets-logo.ico" class="w-6 h-6 object-contain" loading="lazy" alt=""/>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-medium text-gray-900 text-sm">Gaplets</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Scheduling SaaS</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-700 italic leading-relaxed text-sm">
          "The cancellation recovery and replacement logic is what makes the system valuable. Empty slots stopped being silent losses."
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>